*ethereal-0.9.5 (28 Jun 2002)

  28 Jun 2002; Bruce A. Locke <blocke@shivan.org> ethereal-0.9.5.ebuild:

  Bumped the version to 0.9.5 and removed older versions.  Older versions
  had a buffer overflow in various modules and should no longer be used.

